  "_comment_aligned": "Imagery-aligned NorthMacedonia airports: each runway center moved onto the USED runway centerline measured from the installed ortho t{CC}{RR}.dds with align_runways_nm.py (Canny+HoughLinesP robust fit, fallback luminance PCA), cross-checked vs OSM ends azimuth. Glider spawns ON this axis with zero lateral offset (verified Stenkovec convention), so it now lands on the strip. Headings are whole-degree-safe (generate_apt rounds). Widths kept (they drive the tug). Ends translated by the same lateral vector."
